{"tid":619725,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[我們不要tap in人] 拜仁堅稱無意簽C朗","createTime":"2018-04-07T02:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T10:00:08.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11198fb3dfb36c0c7f3ac48a65e41ce417f2feaa","tid":619725,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度被馬德里政府指控逃稅，之後隨即傳出他打算離隊他投的傳聞，當中連球壇班霸拜仁慕尼黑亦榜上有名，不過這支德甲勁旅已經即時公開否認。<br />\n<br />\n面對C朗拿度可能加盟的傳聞，拜仁行政總裁路明尼加即斥消息不實：「近日媒體上關於拜仁的轉會傳聞並非事實。互聯網時代資訊散播非常快，不過有時內容並非真確。一般來說，我們不會就傳聞回應，但今次我們想強調拜仁絕對與C朗拿度沒有關係，這傳聞完全是個笑話。」<br />\n<br />\n如果C朗拿度真的因為官非而避走馬德里，普遍相信他下一站最大可能是舊東家曼聯或法甲的巴黎聖日耳門。"},{"pid":"e7886223236c9ff53f06bfc0097ab07495977542","tid":619725,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:29:20.000Z","msg":"沙拉換牙朗"},{"pid":"cd48b60ff6fa089d63f3d8fa1175689617a710e1","tid":619725,"uid":10392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"傑志都堅稱無意簽C朗"},{"pid":"2db90c9069a8cd1e95bb6a6dae6b558cca600395","tid":619725,"uid":99403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:46:15.000Z","msg":"養老拜超不了"},{"pid":"6a10b0569017c8e15ad5f0a4e61cf905a23954c9","tid":619725,"uid":22345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:15:07.000Z","msg":"咁要唔要走梅拿先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a273ed77f35d3996f20726c733cf1dd2d21a38a9","tid":619725,"uid":2500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"我隊業餘波都無意簽c朗"},{"pid":"7b4272314276a0413542fd4707bbe4fb23423177","tid":619725,"uid":11081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"報紙佬又呃稿費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前就吹回歸獌聯，依家吹到拜超"},{"pid":"0f11021b8ac5d3679b971c6b417eca729d5fd894","tid":619725,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"紐卡索"},{"pid":"ab145a8c8913131f2987b8ee68a864b61a6ec22b","tid":619725,"uid":166126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:00:08.000Z","msg":"拜仁慕尼黑與皇家馬德里的歐洲德比即將打響，在最近的採訪中拜仁慕尼黑董事會主席魯梅尼格高度稱讚了對手皇家馬德里。<br />\n<br />\n魯梅尼格在拜仁的雜誌中稱讚皇家馬德里：&ldquo;如果人們要問我歐洲足球的排名的話，那麼我的回答一如既往：皇家馬德里是第一。整個世界都知道皇家馬德里，並且為這個白色的芭蕾所傾倒。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過魯梅尼格也表示目前的拜仁主帥安切洛蒂是這次對決的加分項，因為安切洛蒂曾經在皇馬執教。魯梅尼格：&ldquo;安切洛蒂曾經在2014年帶領皇家馬德里擊敗馬競獲得歐冠冠軍。或許他是我們在四分之一決賽中重要的加分項。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sport1.de/fussball/champions-league/2017/03/fc-bayern-real-madrid-fuer-karl-heinz-rummenigge-die-nummer-eins\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sport1.de%2Ffussball%2Fchampions-league%2F2017%2F03%2Ffc-bayern-real-madrid-fuer-karl-heinz-rummenigge-die-nummer-eins&d=S3axBjbT7DzXQv2YFLyEHTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=7b88bff8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sport1.de/fussball/champions-league/2017/03/fc-bayern-real-madrid-fuer-karl-heinz-rummenigge-die-nummer-eins</a>"}]}